---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const { locale, dir, t } = Astro.locals;
const updated = "June 29, 2026";
---

<Layout locale={locale} dir={dir} t={t}>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-foreground/80">
    <a href="/" class="text-sm text-[#E8A840] hover:text-[#F5D06A] transition-colors">&larr; Back to NoorJyoti</a>
    <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl text-[#F5D06A] mt-8 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-foreground/50 mb-10">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 leading-relaxed">
      <p>Welcome to NoorJyoti. By accessing or using NoorJyoti (the "Service"), you agree to these
      Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use the Service.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#E8A840] pt-4">The service</h2>
      <p>NoorJyoti provides free access to public-domain scripture texts read aloud in AI-generated
      voices across multiple languages, for personal, devotional, and educational use. An optional
      premium subscription may offer additional features.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#E8A840] pt-4">Content & intellectual property</h2>
      <p>The underlying scripture texts are in the public domain. The AI voice renderings, audio
      compilations, translations of site copy, design, and the NoorJyoti name and marks are owned by
      NoorJyoti. You may listen to and share links to the Service, but you may not scrape, bulk-download,
      resell, or redistribute the audio or content at scale without our written permission.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#E8A840] pt-4">AI-generated audio</h2>
      <p>Audio is produced by automated text-to-speech and may occasionally contain mispronunciations or
      errors. NoorJyoti is intended for listening and reflection and is not a substitute for an
      authoritative printed scripture or scholarly or religious guidance.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#E8A840] pt-4">Acceptable use</h2>
      <p>You agree not to use the Service unlawfully, to disrupt or attempt to gain unauthorized access
      to it, or to use it in any way that infringes the rights of others or misrepresents the content.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#E8A840] pt-4">Subscriptions</h2>
      <p>If you purchase a premium subscription, it renews on a recurring basis until cancelled. You can
      cancel at any time, effective at the end of the current billing period. Except where required by
      law, payments are non-refundable.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#E8A840] pt-4">Disclaimer & limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>The Service is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties of any kind. To the
      fullest extent permitted by law, NoorJyoti is not liable for any indirect, incidental, or
      consequential damages arising from your use of the Service.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#E8A840] pt-4">Changes</h2>
      <p>We may update these Terms from time to time. Continued use of the Service after changes take
      effect constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#E8A840] pt-4">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these Terms? Email
      <a href="mailto:hello@noorjyoti.app" class="text-[#E8A840] hover:text-[#F5D06A]">hello@noorjyoti.app</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
